    • getWasmMnemonic

      @Nullable public static @Nullable String getWasmMnemonic(byte byteOpcode, int intOpcode)
      Look up the mnemonic for a WebAssembly instruction.
      Parameters:
      byteOpcode - The first byte of the instruction.
      intOpcode - Zero if the instruction is one byte, otherwise the LEB128 decoding of the tail of the opcode.
      Returns:
      The mnemonic of the instruction, or null if not found.
